  "text": "language\nSkip to main content\nPRO\nPro indicator: A premium offering that requires a paid subscription.\nAmson安生｜數位行銷 x IG變現\nHome\nContacts\nAutomation\nManychat AI\nInbox\n2\nSettings\nMy Profile\nHelp\nSettings\nMain\nGeneral\nNotifications\nTeam Members\nLogs\nDisplay\nBilling\nSubscriptions\nInvoices\nPayment Details\nInbox\nInbox Behavior\nAuto-Assignment\nChannels\nInstagram\nTikTok\nWhatsApp\nMessenger\nSMS\nEmail\nTelegram\nAutomation\nFields\nTags\nConversion Events\nExtensions\nAPI\nApps\nIntegrations\nPayments\nInstalled Templates\nPixel\n'Notify Assignees' ActionPRO\nMessenger\nSMS\nEmail\nMobile push notification\nTelegram \n\nEnable to let Manychat send you notifications when a contact performs a specific action in your broadcasts, welcome messages, opt-in messages, etc.\n\nDownload Manychat application to receive push notifications and stay informed.\n\nInbox Desktop Notifications\nNotify me when\nI get a new message from a conversation assigned to me\nThere is a new conversation in unassigned folder\nA conversation is assigned to me\nEnable instant popup notifications on your desktop about new messages and assigned conversations. If you don't see the notifications, check your system settings if notifications are on.\nInbox Channel Notifications\nNotify me when\nA conversation is assigned to me\nInbox notifications help you support your audience and track leads across the connected channels below, like Email, SMS, and Telegram.\nMy Telegram for Notifications\nSubscribe With Telegram\nOpt-in to our bot to be able to receive bot notifications in Telegram\nMy Email for Notifications\nUpdate\nMy Phone Number for Notifications\nSave\nI confirm that the phone number is owned by me and I give permission to send me SMS notifications.\nAdd your phone number to receive SMS notifications. Please note that you will be charged for every SMS notification.",
